break_page_1\" data-component-type=\"_break_page_ads\" data-key=\"1\"></div>\n </div>\n <div id=\"flip-image-34446192\" data-component=\"true\" data-component-type=\"image-flip\" data-component-label=\"~\" data-component-front=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2025/11/18/4-1763457987-1763458524.jpg?w=1200&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=-9VKdAzr9t-ohxhOljlaWA\" data-component-back=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2025/11/18/4a-1763457994-1763458525.jpg?w=1200&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=vTL5IPuOi5x7I9SUf8Avwg\" data-component-caption=\"&quot;<p class=\\&quot;Normal\\&quot;>Sau 8 n\\u0103m t\\u00ecm hi\\u1ec3u, \\u0111\\u00f4i trai t\\u00e0i g\\u00e1i s\\u1eafc quy\\u1ebft \\u0111\\u1ecbnh ti\\u1ebfn t\\u1edbi h\\u00f4n nh\\u00e2n b\\u1eb1ng l\\u1ec5 c\\u01b0\\u1edbi ng\\u00e0y 13\\/11.<\\/p> <p class=\\&quot;Normal\\&quot;>Tr\\u00ean trang c\\u00e1 nh\\u00e2n, Minh Khoa h\\u1ea1nh ph\\u00fac chia s\\u1ebb: \\&quot;Tr\\u1eadn n\\u00e0y kh\\u00f4ng c\\u1ea7n VAR, v\\u00ec ch\\u1eafc ch\\u1eafn l\\u00e0 \\u0111\\u00fang ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi r\\u1ed3i. C\\u1ea3m \\u01a1n em \\u0111\\u00e3 v\\u1ec1 chung m\\u1ed9t \\u0111\\u1ed9i. H\\u00e0nh tr\\u00ecnh h\\u1ea1nh ph\\u00fac c\\u1ee7a c\\u1ea7u th\\u1ee7 Minh Khoa ch\\u00ednh th\\u1ee9c sang trang m\\u1edbi. Tr\\u1eadn \\u0111\\u1ea5u quan tr\\u1ecdng nh\\u1ea5t \\u0111\\u1eddi ng\\u01b0\\u1eddi.<\\/p> <p class=\\&quot;Normal\\&quot;>H\\u00f4m nay, Minh Khoa ghi b\\u00e0n th\\u1eafng l\\u1edbn nh\\u1ea5t: r\\u01b0\\u1edbc n\\u00e0ng v\\u1ec1 dinh\\&quot;.<\\/p>&quot;\">\n  <img src=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2025/11/18/4-1763457987-1763458524.jpg?w=1200&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=-9VKdAzr9t-ohxhOljlaWA\">\n </div>\n <div class=\"section-inner outset-column gallery-detail-photo\" id=\"gallery-34447657\">\n  <div class=\"medium-insert-embeds medium-insert-embeds-gallery medium-insert-embeds-normal medium-insert-embeds-large\">\n   <figure>\n    <div class=\"medium-insert