ày, Paula Badosa sẽ chia tay sự nghiệp với gần 10 triệu USD tiền thưởng. Bên cạnh đó, lợi thế ngoại hình của cô còn đem về nhiều hợp đồng quảng cáo. Nike tài trợ trang phục cho Badosa, trong khi Wilson tài trợ dụng cụ thi đấu.</p>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"item_slide_show clearfix\" width=\"768\" height=\"907\" style=\"width: 680px;\" data-json=\"{\" width_:768,_height_:1024}_>\n  <div id=\"slide_show_34447800\" class=\"block_thumb_slide_show\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2025/11/19/paula-badosa-confirms-sexy-singl-1763534129.jpg?w=220&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=VDOTN2Wy89zAGehMjo95ZQ\" data-src=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2025/11/19/paula-badosa-confirms-sexy-singl-1763534129.jpg?w=0&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=DQQUiPzzCk9MXd53DccGIA\" data-size-image=\"true\" style=\"padding-bottom: 133.38235294118%; \">\n   <div class=\"block_thumb_picture\">\n    <picture>\n     <!--[if IE 9]><video style=\"display: none;\"><![endif]-->\n     <source data-srcset=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2025/11/19/paula-badosa-confirms-sexy-singl-1763534129.jpg?w=1200&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=YqE8A89Bd6_hSzKKJUxxZg 1x, https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2025/11/19/paula-badosa-confirms-sexy-singl-1763534129.jpg?w=1200&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=2&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=kEF4DvI7gSXSWj4vR5asxg 2x\"> <!--[if IE 9]></video><![endif]-->\n     <img itemprop=\"contentUrl\" style=\"transform: translateX(-50%); left: 50%;\" loading=\"lazy\" intrinsicsize=\"1200x0\" alt=\"\" class=\"lazy\" src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" data-src=\"https://i1-thethao.vnecdn.net/2025/11/19/paula-badosa-confirms-sexy-singl-1763534129.jpg?w=1200&amp;h=0&amp;q=100&amp;dpr=1&amp;fit=crop&amp;s=YqE8A89Bd6_hSzKKJUxxZg\">\n    </picture>\n   </div>\n   <div class=\"action_thumb flexbox hidden\">\n    <a href=\"javascript:;\" class=\"vne_share_fb\" data-url=\"https://vnexpress.net/nu-than-